            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "id": 6260986,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 景碩(3189)大漲7.09%，報158.5元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>景碩(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3189:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3189\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3189-TW</a>)05日10:21股價上漲10.5元，報158.5元，漲幅7.09%，成交26,841張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>景碩(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3189:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3189\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3189-TW</a>)所屬產業為半導體業，主要業務為電子零組件製造業。電子材料批發業。電子材料零售業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲4.96%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.88%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+5,380 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+2,711 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+361 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+2,308 張</li> <li>融資增減：+2,623 張</li> <li>融券增減：+123 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
